# Exclude internal-only files from distribution archives.
#
# `git archive` (used by GitHub for source-zip downloads, and by most
# ProcessWire module install paths under the hood) honours these
# `export-ignore` directives. The files stay in the repo for development
# but are stripped from any generated archive.
#
# Convention: anything prefixed with `_` is internal-only and not
# intended for end users of the distributed module.

_docs/                  export-ignore
.gitattributes          export-ignore
